{"tid":513262,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【Bitcoin狂潮】印度財政部：加密貨幣等同龐氏騙局！","createTime":"2017-12-29T10:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T08:22:13.000Z","uid":17738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"417ad342ef995ababc62bd9e69150ec170b168ea","tid":513262,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171229/large/1514537695_3e86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171229%2Flarge%2F1514537695_3e86.jpg&h=9f4da01a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度財政部發公告，向比特幣（Bitcoin）等加密貨幣的投資者作出風險警告，指加密貨幣的投資如同「龐氏騙局」，投資者最好避免參與其中，否則需要完全承擔風險。<br />\n<br />\n印度財政部在聲明稱，加密貨幣在印度不是法定貨幣和不受保護，但未有宣佈完全禁止加密貨幣和作出任何限制。<br />\n聲明又指加密貨幣的投資泡沫風險還在加大，並可能會有突如其來和持續的崩盤，而交易可能會被用於非法活動，如助長恐怖主義、走私、販毒及其他洗黑錢活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171229/57640503\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171229%2F57640503&d=PyvhatFNHvf0VQZCNupr9jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2bd632a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171229%2F57640503&h=fa0c7fb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171229/57640503</a>"},{"pid":"4ce0325591d37b5c04b6481b759f543fd48b3ad8","tid":513262,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"全球政府開始封殺bitcoin 了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79574561fa6c3a6956b08608c3f304f914fa0474","tid":513262,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0d8b9c17991e8ff220ed86ecb354352d9cca6c","tid":513262,"uid":53429,"like":0,"dislike":0